<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's impossible. Out of the question.</b></font>

161
00:12:54,134 --> 00:12:57,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wouldn't be in a bind if I could do that.</b></font>

162
00:12:57,384 --> 00:13:01,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've tried many times. I just wuss out at the last second.</b></font>

163
00:13:01,064 --> 00:13:02,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Once you miss your chance,</b></font>

164
00:13:02,974 --> 00:13:04,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>it's over.</b></font>

165
00:13:04,434 --> 00:13:06,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No kidding.</b></font>

166
00:13:06,984 --> 00:13:11,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've lost track of how many times I wanted to call Kazumi-chan.</b></font>

167
00:13:11,324 --> 00:13:15,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You gradually lose your opportunities to make a move as time goes by...</b></font>

168
00:13:16,764 --> 00:13:19,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's already been half a year since then.</b></font>

169
00:13:19,534 --> 00:13:21,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's the problem with half a year?</b></font>

170
00:13:21,494 --> 00:13:24,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's too late.</b></font>

171
00:13:24,844 --> 00:13:28,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's no way a cute girl like that would stay single for long.</b></font>

172
00:13:28,214 --> 00:13:30,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You don't know that.</b></font>

173
00:13:30,844 --> 00:13:34,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Mako-chan isn't the same as those typical light-hearted girls.</b></font>

174
00:13:34,344 --> 00:13:37,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>She wouldn't like it if I called her!</b></font>

175
00:13:39,754 --> 00:13:42,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Anyway, it's too late.</b></font>

176
00:13:43,084 --> 00:13:45,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm convinced of that much.</b></font>

177
00:13:48,954 --> 00:13:51,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's really holding it back.</b></font>

178
00:13:51,864 --> 00:13:56,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I guess he needs some fated encounter to break him out.</b></font>

179
00:14:08,734 --> 00:14:13,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A day hasn't gone by when I haven't thought of Mako-chan.</b></font>

180
00:14:15,024 --> 00:14:20,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've always thought that I need to apologize about that day.</b></font>

181
00:14:22,604 --> 00:14:27,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But you know what, Moon? That's what's so hard about this...</b></font>

182
00:14:28,734 --> 00:14:29,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Huh?</b></font>

183
00:14:31,864 --> 00:14:32,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, a shooting star!</b></font>

184
00:14:44,074 --> 00:14:48,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Man, a memorial service? What a drag.</b></font>

185
00:14:50,354 --> 00:14:52,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's kinda busy.</b></font>

186
00:14:52,374 --> 00:14:54,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is it because it's a holiday?</b></font>

187
00:14:54,444 --> 00:14:56,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Say, Koichirou.</b></font>

188
00:14:56,194 --> 00:14:56,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Huh?</b></font>

189
00:14:56,924 --> 00:14:58,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is there a rest area coming up?</b></font>

190
00:14:58,804 --> 00:15:00,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?</b></font>

191
00:15:00,044 --> 00:15:01,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Can't be helped I guess...</b></font>

192
00:15:08,914 --> 00:15:10,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hurry up, Mom!</b></font>

193
00:15:10,304 --> 00:15:12,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We don't have a lot of time.</b></font>

194
00:15:12,024 --> 00:15:14,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, yeah, I know.</b></font>

195
00:15:14,154 --> 00:15:15,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sheesh.</b></font>

196
00:15:19,024 --> 00:15:21,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The rest of the world is on vacation, huh.</b></font>

197
00:15:24,084 --> 00:15:26,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There are couples everywhere I look!</b></font>

198
00:15:26,794 --> 00:15:28,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So where do you wanna go after that?</b></font>

199
00:15:29,364 --> 00:15:31,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, anywhere's fine!</b></font>

200
00:15:31,644 --> 00:15:35,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I want to go on a drive with a girl like that too.</b></font>

201
00:15:35,254 --> 00:15:39,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>To think that the person sitting in the passenger's seat for my roadtrip is my mom...</b></font>

202
00:15:42,224 --> 00:15:45,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's depressing to the megaton-level.</b></font>

203
00:15:47,124 --> 00:15:49,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What is it, Mom?</b></font>

204
00:15:49,934 --> 00:15:51,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Stare...</b></font>

205
00:15:54,914 --> 00:15:56,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just as I thought! It's Iketani!</b></font>

206
00:15:56,704 --> 00:15:58,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>S-Sayuki-chan!</b></font>

207
00:15:58,444 --> 00:16:02,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I thought it was someone else because you were dressed like that.</b></font>

208
00:16:02,334 --> 00:16:05,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey Mako! It was Iketani after all!</b></font>

209
00:16:05,204 --> 00:16:07,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What are you doing? Come over here already!</b></font>

210
00:16:08,844 --> 00:16:10,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Mako-chan?</b></font>

211
00:16:17,794 --> 00:16:19,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hello.</b></font>

212
00:16:21,714 --> 00:16:23,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I-it's been awhile.</b></font>

213
00:16:23,834 --> 00:16:26,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, what are you getting flustered for?</b></font>

214
00:16:26,494 --> 00:16:28,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You sure are a weird man.</b></font>

215
00:16:28,584 --> 00:16:30,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>W-well...</b></font>

216
00:16:30,364 --> 00:16:32,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But man, this brings back memories. How's everyone doing?</b></font>

217
00:16:32,854 --> 00:16:34,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Y-yeah...</b></font>

218
00:16:36,904 --> 00:16:39,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi-kun's sure amazing!</b></font>

219
00:16:39,024 --> 00:16:42,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've been making sure to check Project D's home page.</b></font>

220
00:16:44,744 --> 00:16:47,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is this reality?</b></font>

221
00:16:47,244 --> 00:16:50,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is that really Mako-chan in front of me?</b></font>

222
00:16:52,584 --> 00:16:53,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>At 8pm...</b></font>

223
00:16:55,974 --> 00:16:59,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll be waiting for you under the billboard...</b></font>

224
00:17:01,664 --> 00:17:02,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>that I first met you at.</b></font>

225
00:17:04,044 --> 00:17:05,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Would you like to meet there</b></font>

226
00:17:06,404 --> 00:17:13,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and spend the night together somewhere quiet, where we can be alone?</b></font>

227
00:17:16,064 --> 00:17:18,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Mako-chan is...</b></font>

228
00:17:18,204 --> 00:17:20,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Mako-chan is right in front of my eyes...</b></font>

229
00:17:21,154 --> 00:17:23,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey now, Iketani,</b></font>

230
00:17:23,464 --> 00:17:25,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>have you been listening to me at all?</b></font>

231
00:17:25,514 --> 00:17:26,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Huh?</b></font>

232
00:17:26,164 --> 00:17:28,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's the matter with you, spacing out like that?</b></font>

233
00:17:28,664 --> 00:17:31,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh sorry, Sayuki-chan.</b></font>

234
00:17:31,134 --> 00:17:34,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I just remembered that there was something I just had to tell Mako-chan.</b></font>

235
00:17:34,664 --> 00:17:36,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Huh?!</b></font>

236
00:17:37,874 --> 00:17:41,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I... need to apologize to you, Mako-chan.</b></font>

237
00:17:41,084 --> 00:17:42,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm really sorry</b></font>

238
00:17:42,604 --> 00:17:45,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>for not making it to our meeting on time.</b></font>

239
00:17:46,594 --> 00:17:49,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>On that day, the highway was really backed up.</b></font>

240
00:17:49,514 --> 00:17:52,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, it wasn't just that.</b></font>

241
00:17:52,174 --> 00:17:55,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's also because I left late.</b></font>

242
00:17:55,414 --> 00:17:58,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Either way, it was past 10</b></font>

243
00:17:58,404 --> 00:18:00,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>by the time I got to our meeting spot.</b></font>

244
00:18:00,234 --> 00:18:02,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What? You can't be serious...</b></font>

245
00:18:02,364 --> 00:18:05,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I waited there until 10pm exactly.</b></font>

246
00:18:05,744 --> 00:18:07,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No!</b></font>

247
00:18:07,054 --> 00:18:08,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You must be joking.</b></font>

248
00:18:08,764 --> 00:18:12,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Mako-chan, you waited two hours for someone like me?!</b></font>

249
00:18:12,684 --> 00:18:13,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes.</b></font>

250
00:18:13,744 --> 00:18:16,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So back then...</b></font>

251
00:18:17,814 --> 00:18:21,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Could it be that I missed her...</b></font>

252
00:18:21,694 --> 00:18:23,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>by just a minute or two?!</b></font>

253
00:18:26,424 --> 00:18:29,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I really must've been out of luck.</b></font>

254
00:18:29,554 --> 00:18:30,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No,</b></font>

255
00:18:30,524 --> 00:18:34,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>if I hadn't hesitated back then and left sooner...</b></font>

256
00:18:34,914 --> 00:18:36,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Koichirou, what are you doing?</b></font>

257
00:18:37,574 --> 00:18:38,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Gah!</b></font>

258
00:18:38,744 --> 00:18:39,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Mom?!</b></font>

259
00:18:39,854 --> 00:18:41,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's nothing at all!</b></font>

260
00:18:41,684 --> 00:18:44,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, we'll be late if we don't get going.</b></font>

261
00:18:44,594 --> 00:18:46,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Your aunts will nag us.</b></font>

262
00:18:46,444 --> 00:18:47,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know that!</b></font>

263
00:18:47,994 --> 00:18:52,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll be right there, so you don't need to come over here. You're embarrassing me!</b></font>

264
00:18:53,164 --> 00:18:54,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>God dammit!</b></font>

265
00:18:54,604 --> 00:18:56,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why do things always go like this?</b></font>

266
00:18:56,484 --> 00:18:59,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My head's starting to spin,</b></font>

267
00:18:59,184 --> 00:19:00,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but I'm not gonna back down!</b></font>

268
00:19:05,634 --> 00:19:06,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Mako-chan,</b></font>

269
00:19:06,884 --> 00:19:10,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I have other things I want to tell you,</b></font>

270
00:19:10,224 --> 00:19:12,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but I don't have time today.</b></font>

271
00:19:12,354 --> 00:19:13,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Um...</b></font>

272
00:19:13,924 --> 00:19:15,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so...</b></font>

273
00:19:15,644 --> 00:19:16,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I...</b></font>

274
00:19:17,344 --> 00:19:18,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Me too.</b></font>

275
00:19:19,054 --> 00:19:22,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I have something I want to tell you too, Iketani-san.</b></font>

276
00:19:23,364 --> 00:19:26,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Please give me a call when you get the time.</b></font>

277
00:19:26,804 --> 00:19:28,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll be waiting.</b></font>

278
00:19:28,074 --> 00:19:30,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>M-Mako-chan...</b></font>

279
00:19:30,124 --> 00:19:32,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I got it! I'll be sure to contact you.</b></font>

280
00:19:32,954 --> 00:19:34,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>W-well then...</b></font>

281
00:19:34,694 --> 00:19:36,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah. See you again.</b></font>

282
00:19:43,074 --> 00:19:45,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, what's the matter, Koichirou?</b></font>

283
00:19:45,974 --> 00:19:47,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Who's that girl?</b></font>

284
00:19:51,884 --> 00:19:54,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, Koichirou...</b></font>

285
00:19:54,244 --> 00:19:55,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey...</b></font>

286
00:19:56,414 --> 00:19:59,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't remember how I got back to the car.</b></font>

287
00:19:59,564 --> 00:20:04,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My mind was blown for the next 30 minutes.</b></font>

288
00:20:18,794 --> 00:20:21,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I have no doubts about it.</b></font>

289
00:20:22,954 --> 00:20:26,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This was surely destiny.</b></font>

290
00:20:36,584 --> 00:20:37,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?!</b></font>

291
00:20:37,894 --> 00:20:40,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You met Mako-chan?</b></font>

292
00:20:40,054 --> 00:20:42,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is that true, Iketani-senpai?</b></font>

293
00:20:42,454 --> 00:20:44,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's right.</b></font>

294
00:20:44,034 --> 00:20:46,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Really, really, really for real.</b></font>

295
00:20:46,524 --> 00:20:49,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't believe such a coincidence could happen.</b></font>

296
00:20:49,994 --> 00:20:53,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I ran right into her at a rest area on the highway.</b></font>

297
00:20:53,474 --> 00:20:54,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I see...</b></font>

298
00:20:54,784 --> 00:20:58,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm convinced for sure this time.</b></font>

299
00:20:59,624 --> 00:21:04,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is my "last chance" that's been given to me by my revered ancestors.</b></font>

300
00:21:04,244 --> 00:21:05,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>D'oh!</b></font>

301
00:21:05,244 --> 00:21:07,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why is it your ancestors?</b></font>

302
00:21:07,374 --> 00:21:11,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Iketani-senpai, I thought your word of choice was "God"?</b></font>

303
00:21:11,054 --> 00:21:15,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Not this time, because I was on my way to a memorial service.</b></font>

304
00:21:15,264 --> 00:21:18,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This guy has a surprisingly religious side to him.</b></font>

305
00:21:18,264 --> 00:21:24,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can tell that time is being rewound at an incredible pace inside me right now.</b></font>

306
00:21:25,234 --> 00:21:28,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's as if I'm in a time machine!</b></font>

307
00:21:28,274 --> 00:21:29,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Huh.</b></font>

308
00:21:29,674 --> 00:21:35,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's as if I can almost go back to under that Kamameshi restaurant billboard.</b></font>

309
00:21:37,214 --> 00:21:39,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thank you, revered ancestors.</b></font>

310
00:21:39,874 --> 00:21:43,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I... will never repeat the same mistake!</b></font>

311
00:21:43,374 --> 00:21:44,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's right.</b></font>

312
00:21:44,514 --> 00:21:45,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Good luck!</b></font>

313
00:21:45,554 --> 00:21:46,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah!</b></font>

314
00:21:46,484 --> 00:21:52,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My difficulties of the past six months have drilled into me the importance of acting with courage.</b></font>

315
00:21:52,914 --> 00:21:54,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll score for sure this time.</b></font>

316
00:21:54,634 --> 00:21:57,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm going to make a move on Mako-chan!</b></font>

317
00:21:59,784 --> 00:22:00,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>An aura!</b></font>

318
00:22:00,754 --> 00:22:02,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's emitting an aura!!</b></font>

319
00:22:06,374 --> 00:22:09,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm not sure what's going on, but you're impressing me.</b></font>

320
00:22:09,154 --> 00:22:11,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You've sure grown.</b></font>

321
00:22:11,614 --> 00:22:15,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't believe you're the same indecisive Iketani.</b></font>

322
00:22:15,444 --> 00:22:17,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, really.</b></font>

323
00:22:17,184 --> 00:22:18,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Things really worked out.</b></font>

324
00:22:18,834 --> 00:22:20,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm happy for you, Iketani.</b></font>

325
00:22:20,164 --> 00:22:22,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Good luck this time.</b></font>

326
00:22:22,344 --> 00:22:24,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I think you definitely have a shot.</b></font>

327
00:22:24,104 --> 00:22:26,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Make sure you get your beloved Mako-chan!</b></font>

328
00:22:29,004 --> 00:22:30,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Whoa.</b></font>

329
00:22:30,504 --> 00:22:32,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He sure seems confident.</b></font>

330
00:22:46,414 --> 00:22:47,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why?</b></font>

331
00:22:47,784 --> 00:22:50,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why am I hesitating at the last moment?</b></font>

332
00:22:51,424 --> 00:22:54,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't decide. What am I supposed to do?</b></font>

333
00:23:01,284 --> 00:23:02,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Mako.</b></font>

334
00:23:02,784 --> 00:23:04,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's a car coming up.</b></font>

335
00:23:05,144 --> 00:23:05,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay.</b></font>

336
00:23:09,834 --> 00:23:11,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Did you see that?</b></font>

337
00:23:11,474 --> 00:23:13,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They were women.</b></font>

338
00:23:13,154 --> 00:23:14,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh?</b></font>

339
00:23:14,404 --> 00:23:16,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Female racers, huh?</b></font>

340
00:23:26,804 --> 00:23:28,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Not bad...</b></font>

341
00:23:29,264 --> 00:23:31,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but you should be able to go faster.</b></font>

342
00:23:31,024 --> 00:23:32,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay.</b></font>

343
00:23:33,004 --> 00:23:34,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll go for another run.</b></font>

344
00:23:46,534 --> 00:23:48,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Here they come, here they come.</b></font>

345
00:23:57,924 --> 00:24:00,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, missies!</b></font>

346
00:24:01,624 --> 00:24:03,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey!</b></font>

347
00:24:10,104 --> 00:24:12,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're looking pretty good.</b></font>

348
00:24:12,654 --> 00:24:16,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Say, won't you give us a tip or two?</b></font>

349
00:24:21,114 --> 00:24:23,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey now, you're gonna totally ignore us?</b></font>

350
00:24:23,584 --> 00:24:25,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hah! Acting so stuck up...</b></font>

351
00:24:25,974 --> 00:24:28,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>you two probably came up here looking for men.</b></font>

352
00:24:28,624 --> 00:24:32,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They must be full of themselves just because they can drive a little.</b></font>

353
00:24:32,124 --> 00:24:35,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Drive? They're just women in the end.</b></font>

354
00:24:36,424 --> 00:24:38,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So what if we're female?</b></font>

355
00:24:38,134 --> 00:24:41,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, now she's heating up.</b></font>

356
00:24:42,384 --> 00:24:47,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Getting looked down on just for being female pisses us off like nothing else.</b></font>

357
00:24:47,264 --> 00:24:49,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How scary!</b></font>

358
00:24:49,014 --> 00:24:52,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So, you wanna race us?</b></font>

359
00:24:52,574 --> 00:24:54,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A single downhill run.</b></font>

360
00:24:55,284 --> 00:24:57,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What do you think, Mako?</b></font>

361
00:24:57,184 --> 00:25:00,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If we don't accept, they'll say we ran away because we're women.</b></font>

362
00:25:00,484 --> 00:25:02,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's the way! Let's do it.</b></font>

363
00:25:02,874 --> 00:25:03,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

364
00:25:04,594 --> 00:25:08,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We'll go with the leader-chaser format.
Leave the other in the dust or overtake to win.</b></font>

365
00:25:08,074 --> 00:25:10,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You guys can lead.</b></font>

366
00:25:11,514 --> 00:25:12,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>All right.</b></font>

367
00:25:12,844 --> 00:25:14,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's have them cry like babies.</b></font>

368
00:25:17,274 --> 00:25:19,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's go then!</b></font>

369
00:25:29,224 --> 00:25:32,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do those women really think that they can beat me?</b></font>

370
00:25:32,814 --> 00:25:34,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What should we do when we win?</b></font>

371
00:25:34,524 --> 00:25:36,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Maybe we can get some...</b></font>

372
00:25:41,444 --> 00:25:42,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Good,</b></font>

373
00:25:42,474 --> 00:25:44,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>we'll let them run for a little bit.</b></font>

374
00:25:45,294 --> 00:25:48,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We'll take it to them at the exit of corner C-121 like usual.</b></font>

375
00:25:48,164 --> 00:25:49,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay.</b></font>

376
00:26:05,634 --> 00:26:07,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're better than we thought.</b></font>

377
00:26:07,324 --> 00:26:08,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah,</b></font>

378
00:26:08,464 --> 00:26:09,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but...</b></font>

379
00:26:10,674 --> 00:26:12,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>they're not anyone I'd lose to.</b></font>

380
00:26:15,344 --> 00:26:17,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, start trying a little.</b></font>

381
00:26:17,414 --> 00:26:18,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're sticking right to us!</b></font>

382
00:26:19,774 --> 00:26:21,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is impossible.</b></font>

383
00:26:22,254 --> 00:26:23,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's going on?</b></font>

384
00:26:29,024 --> 00:26:30,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Amazing.</b></font>

385
00:26:30,344 --> 00:26:32,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're amazing, Mako.</b></font>

386
00:26:32,124 --> 00:26:36,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're definitely faster than when we raced against Takumi-kun.</b></font>

387
00:26:39,104 --> 00:26:41,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Your entry speed into corners,</b></font>

388
00:26:41,334 --> 00:26:44,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>braking, choice of lines...</b></font>

389
00:26:44,714 --> 00:26:46,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>they're all perfect.</b></font>

390
00:26:58,574 --> 00:27:01,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We don't need to wait until C-121.</b></font>

391
00:27:01,974 --> 00:27:03,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm passing him on the next corner!</b></font>

392
00:27:11,574 --> 00:27:13,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>N-no way!</b></font>

393
00:27:13,444 --> 00:27:14,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey!</b></font>

394
00:27:26,054 --> 00:27:27,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Unbelievable!</b></font>

395
00:27:36,994 --> 00:27:39,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You've become independent, Mako...</b></font>

396
00:28:48,734 --> 00:28:50,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well then, Kenji, Itsuki,</b></font>

397
00:28:50,964 --> 00:28:52,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll be on my way.</b></font>

398
00:28:52,514 --> 00:28:53,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?</b></font>

399
00:28:53,214 --> 00:28:54,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Already?</b></font>

400
00:28:54,574 --> 00:28:56,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You sure are leaving early.</b></font>

401
00:28:56,744 --> 00:28:59,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Weren't you meeting her at night?</b></font>

402
00:28:59,144 --> 00:29:01,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't be careful enough.</b></font>

403
00:29:01,984 --> 00:29:06,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>After all, it wouldn't be funny if I was late again today.</b></font>

404
00:29:06,734 --> 00:29:09,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even so, don't you think you're going too soon?</b></font>

405
00:29:09,864 --> 00:29:11,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's fine.</b></font>

406
00:29:11,504 --> 00:29:15,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Mako-chan waited two hours for me.</b></font>

407
00:29:16,164 --> 00:29:20,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you think about that, getting there two hours early is nothing.</b></font>

408
00:29:20,994 --> 00:29:23,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, you have a point when you put it that way.</b></font>

409
00:29:23,544 --> 00:29:25,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Either way, I'm off.</b></font>

410
00:29:25,414 --> 00:29:28,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't fail if I'm a step ahead on every move.</b></font>

411
00:29:29,644 --> 00:29:30,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Good luck!</b></font>

412
00:29:30,904 --> 00:29:32,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hurrah! Hurrah!</b></font>

413
00:29:32,694 --> 00:29:34,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Iketani-senpai!</b></font>

414
00:29:41,714 --> 00:29:42,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So he's gone?</b></font>

415
00:29:42,644 --> 00:29:46,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Iketani-senpai's unbelievably invested in this.</b></font>

416
00:29:46,394 --> 00:29:47,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah,</b></font>

417
00:29:47,564 --> 00:29:50,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>his last mistake must really have smarted.</b></font>

418
00:29:50,524 --> 00:29:52,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wonder what'll happen...</b></font>

419
00:29:52,344 --> 00:29:53,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It makes me nervous.</b></font>

420
00:29:53,614 --> 00:29:58,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>From what I've heard from Iketani, I think he's got a pretty good chance...</b></font>

421
00:29:59,074 --> 00:30:03,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It sounds like Mako-chan was waiting all this time for him to contact her too.</b></font>

422
00:30:03,624 --> 00:30:06,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In that case, I think something big's about to happen!</b></font>

423
00:30:08,874 --> 00:30:12,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Iketani had a serious crush on Mako-chan, after all...</b></font>

424
00:30:12,744 --> 00:30:16,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It'd be like a dream for him if a girl like that became his girlfriend.</b></font>

425
00:30:16,804 --> 00:30:19,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The thought of it makes me jealous.</b></font>

426
00:30:19,304 --> 00:30:21,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And what about you, Kenji-senpai?</b></font>

427
00:30:21,854 --> 00:30:26,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well to be honest, I used to be really jealous too.</b></font>

428
00:30:26,014 --> 00:30:28,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Mako-chan's pretty, after all.</b></font>

429
00:30:28,014 --> 00:30:29,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, really.</b></font>

430
00:30:29,204 --> 00:30:31,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's to be expected of any man!</b></font>

431
00:30:31,194 --> 00:30:32,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But you know,</b></font>

432
00:30:32,534 --> 00:30:36,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I truly feel like cheering him on now.</b></font>

433
00:30:36,074 --> 00:30:39,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I get the feeling that I'll get an earful of bragging on a daily basis,</b></font>

434
00:30:39,454 --> 00:30:41,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but I'll take it for his sake.</b></font>

435
00:30:42,724 --> 00:30:46,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're bringing tears to my eye! Now that's a manly friendship!</b></font>

436
00:30:46,004 --> 00:30:49,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I just can't turn my back on him.</b></font>

437
00:30:49,214 --> 00:30:51,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I worry more about him than about myself.</b></font>

438
00:30:51,424 --> 00:30:53,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's true.</b></font>

439
00:30:53,124 --> 00:30:56,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I want Iketani-senpai to find happiness too.</b></font>

440
00:30:56,894 --> 00:30:58,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey now,</b></font>

441
00:30:58,334 --> 00:31:01,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>stop cheering for Iketani...</b></font>

442
00:31:01,164 --> 00:31:05,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and go find a girlfriend or two for yourselves already.</b></font>

443
00:31:05,974 --> 00:31:08,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Youth is short.</b></font>

444
00:31:08,524 --> 00:31:11,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Please don't remind me...</b></font>

445
00:31:12,304 --> 00:31:13,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My heart is aching.</b></font>

446
00:31:13,684 --> 00:31:15,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kazumi-chan...</b></font>

447
00:31:17,384 --> 00:31:19,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And I have no one...</b></font>

448
00:31:30,014 --> 00:31:32,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm surprisingly calm.</b></font>

449
00:31:34,404 --> 00:31:39,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even though I'm about to confess my feelings to a girl for the first time in my life...</b></font>

450
00:31:42,544 --> 00:31:44,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>"Please date me."</b></font>

451
00:31:44,754 --> 00:31:47,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I just need to say that one sentence.</b></font>

452
00:31:47,684 --> 00:31:49,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I have no expectations.</b></font>

453
00:31:49,484 --> 00:31:50,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm just going to throw my everything at her.</b></font>

454
00:31:51,934 --> 00:31:55,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When I think about my half year of constant regret,</b></font>

455
00:31:55,634 --> 00:31:57,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I have no doubts holding me back!</b></font>

456
00:32:10,914 --> 00:32:13,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh boy...</b></font>

457
00:32:13,214 --> 00:32:17,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The highway was empty, so I really did get here two hours early.</b></font>

458
00:32:17,674 --> 00:32:19,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh well.</b></font>

459
00:32:19,364 --> 00:32:22,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Now I'll be 100% on time.</b></font>

460
00:32:22,474 --> 00:32:24,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When I think about the six months leading up to today,</b></font>

461
00:32:24,884 --> 00:32:26,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>two hours is nothing.</b></font>

462
00:32:54,634 --> 00:32:56,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Excuse me...</b></font>

463
00:32:56,194 --> 00:32:56,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Huh?</b></font>

464
00:32:56,964 --> 00:33:00,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I saw that you've been sitting there</b></font>

465
00:33:00,124 --> 00:33:03,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and don't seem to be in a hurry.</b></font>

466
00:33:03,864 --> 00:33:07,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do you think you could listen to what I have to say?</b></font>

467
00:33:13,574 --> 00:33:15,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?!</b></font>

468
00:33:15,064 --> 00:33:18,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Your tour bus left while you were eating some kamameshi?!</b></font>

469
00:33:18,564 --> 00:33:20,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's right.</b></font>

470
00:33:20,194 --> 00:33:23,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So I have a favor to ask of you.</b></font>

471
00:33:23,484 --> 00:33:29,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm very sorry for the trouble, but could you drive me to my hotel in Karuizawa?</b></font>

472
00:33:29,454 --> 00:33:32,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'd really rather not...</b></font>

473
00:33:32,454 --> 00:33:34,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know it's a lot of trouble,</b></font>

474
00:33:34,794 --> 00:33:40,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but I'm not familiar with this area and I don't know my left from my right.</b></font>

475
00:33:40,144 --> 00:33:43,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was really starting to get lonely.</b></font>

476
00:33:47,034 --> 00:33:48,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Won't you?</b></font>

477
00:33:50,004 --> 00:33:51,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>As I expected...</b></font>

478
00:33:52,264 --> 00:33:54,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh man...</b></font>

479
00:33:54,254 --> 00:33:56,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm starting to feel sorry for him.</b></font>

480
00:33:56,024 --> 00:34:01,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I could make it to Karuizawa and back in an hour.</b></font>

481
00:34:03,984 --> 00:34:05,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>All right,</b></font>

482
00:34:05,674 --> 00:34:07,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll take you there, gramps.</b></font>

483
00:34:07,614 --> 00:34:08,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Huh?</b></font>

484
00:34:08,714 --> 00:34:10,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Really?</b></font>

485
00:34:10,014 --> 00:34:11,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, thank you.</b></font>

486
00:34:11,884 --> 00:34:16,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Please, please, you're a good person!</b></font>

487
00:34:16,264 --> 00:34:18,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay, hurry and get in.</b></font>

488
00:34:18,054 --> 00:34:18,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay.</b></font>

489
00:34:30,404 --> 00:34:33,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you traveling by yourself, gramps?</b></font>

490
00:34:33,264 --> 00:34:35,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's right.</b></font>

491
00:34:35,654 --> 00:34:39,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>At my age, traveling is about the only fun in your life.</b></font>

492
00:34:39,024 --> 00:34:40,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I see...</b></font>

493
00:34:40,734 --> 00:34:46,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Spring, summer, fall, winter:</b></font>

494
00:34:46,614 --> 00:34:51,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>they all have their own flavors.</b></font>

495
00:34:51,744 --> 00:34:55,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Now that he mentions it, it's spring already.</b></font>

496
00:34:56,174 --> 00:34:59,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The seasons sure go by quickly.</b></font>

497
00:35:04,464 --> 00:35:08,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh yeah, where in Karuizawa is your hotel, gramps?</b></font>

498
00:35:08,554 --> 00:35:10,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well...</b></font>

499
00:35:10,904 --> 00:35:14,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I think I had a pamphlet.</b></font>

500
00:35:21,134 --> 00:35:22,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, here it is.</b></font>

501
00:35:22,734 --> 00:35:25,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'd like for you to take me here.</b></font>

502
00:35:27,964 --> 00:35:30,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What? Kitakaru Grand Hotel?</b></font>

503
00:35:30,834 --> 00:35:32,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wait a minute, gramps,</b></font>

504
00:35:32,944 --> 00:35:35,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>although it is Karuizawa, this is in North Karuizawa!</b></font>

505
00:35:36,724 --> 00:35:37,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It is Karuizawa, no?</b></font>

506
00:35:37,794 --> 00:35:40,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>North Karuizawa is in Gunma Prefecture.</b></font>

507
00:35:40,344 --> 00:35:43,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's far away! I can't do that.</b></font>

508
00:35:47,714 --> 00:35:51,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't say no to that face!</b></font>

509
00:35:51,294 --> 00:35:54,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Crap, what a nightmare.</b></font>

510
00:35:54,214 --> 00:35:58,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Two hours is barely enough for North Karuizawa...</b></font>

511
00:35:58,934 --> 00:36:02,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Please give me a call when you get the time.</b></font>

512
00:36:02,434 --> 00:36:03,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll be waiting.</b></font>

513
00:36:03,654 --> 00:36:05,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>M-Mako-chan...</b></font>

514
00:36:05,804 --> 00:36:07,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I got it! I'll be sure to contact you.</b></font>

515
00:36:07,904 --> 00:36:09,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>W-well then...</b></font>

516
00:36:09,944 --> 00:36:11,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

517
00:36:11,064 --> 00:36:12,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>See you again.</b></font>

518
00:36:13,734 --> 00:36:18,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, but if I give it my best, I'll be able to get back on time.</b></font>

519
00:36:19,164 --> 00:36:21,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Gramps, I'm gonna step on it.</b></font>

520
00:36:21,184 --> 00:36:22,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Please hang on!</b></font>

521
00:36:59,914 --> 00:37:02,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's not here yet.</b></font>

522
00:37:02,014 --> 00:37:05,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I got here first again.</b></font>

523
00:37:10,004 --> 00:37:12,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm such an idiot!</b></font>

524
00:37:13,844 --> 00:37:15,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Half a year ago,</b></font>

525
00:37:15,664 --> 00:37:17,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I messed everything up by being two hours late.</b></font>

526
00:37:18,274 --> 00:37:21,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Today, I messed up by being two hours early.</b></font>

527
00:37:21,844 --> 00:37:24,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is too much, revered ancestors!</b></font>

528
00:37:35,244 --> 00:37:38,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If only I was Takumi at a time like this...</b></font>

529
00:37:45,004 --> 00:37:46,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Shit!</b></font>

530
00:37:49,044 --> 00:37:50,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Either way, I need to hurry.</b></font>

531
00:37:50,644 --> 00:37:53,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If I speed, I should only be about 30 minutes late.</b></font>

532
00:37:54,724 --> 00:37:58,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've trained my driving technique for a time like this!</b></font>

533
00:39:01,014 --> 00:39:03,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I... I've done it...</b></font>

534
00:39:03,854 --> 00:39:06,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I hit a rock on the shoulder of the road...</b></font>

535
00:39:06,664 --> 00:39:07,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and burst a tire.</b></font>

536
00:39:07,884 --> 00:39:09,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is the worst!</b></font>

537
00:39:13,234 --> 00:39:14,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't have a spare!</b></font>

538
00:39:25,854 --> 00:39:30,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You should at least change your right rear tire though.</b></font>

539
00:39:30,444 --> 00:39:31,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's right!</b></font>

540
00:39:31,804 --> 00:39:33,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I changed my tire back then and...</b></font>

541
00:39:33,314 --> 00:39:34,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Shit!</b></font>

542
00:39:34,824 --> 00:39:36,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And at a time like this!</b></font>

543
00:39:37,644 --> 00:39:40,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh yeah, I need to call her at least...</b></font>

544
00:39:44,704 --> 00:39:47,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why is my battery out?!</b></font>

545
00:39:48,794 --> 00:39:50,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't waste time here!</b></font>

546
00:39:53,714 --> 00:39:55,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Mako-chan, I'm so sorry!</b></font>

547
00:39:55,734 --> 00:40:00,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Mako-chan!</b></font>

548
00:40:11,224 --> 00:40:13,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wonder what happened to Iketani-san...?</b></font>

549
00:40:13,854 --> 00:40:16,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's not even calling.</b></font>

550
00:40:16,144 --> 00:40:17,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wonder...</b></font>

551
00:40:17,314 --> 00:40:19,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>if he forgot?</b></font>

552
00:40:28,944 --> 00:40:32,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's not even a public phone in the mountains like this.</b></font>

553
00:40:36,254 --> 00:40:37,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ouch...</b></font>

554
00:40:37,964 --> 00:40:39,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>shit.</b></font>

555
00:40:39,444 --> 00:40:41,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My heart's about to burst.</b></font>

556
00:40:41,554 --> 00:40:43,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I need to find a phone!</b></font>

557
00:40:51,804 --> 00:40:55,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A racer is racing down the mountain pass on his own feet...</b></font>

558
00:40:55,854 --> 00:40:57,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This isn't even funny!</b></font>

559
00:41:15,404 --> 00:41:16,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hello?</b></font>

560
00:41:17,794 --> 00:41:19,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Iketani-san!</b></font>

561
00:41:19,334 --> 00:41:21,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm so glad to hear from you. Where are you now?</b></font>

562
00:41:24,084 --> 00:41:26,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Huh? You have a flat?</b></font>

563
00:41:43,424 --> 00:41:46,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm really sorry, Mako-chan.</b></font>

564
00:41:46,574 --> 00:41:49,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Not only was I late, I had to have you come get me...</b></font>

565
00:41:51,004 --> 00:41:53,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm really pathetic.</b></font>

566
00:41:54,054 --> 00:41:56,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, please don't worry about it.</b></font>

567
00:41:56,914 --> 00:41:58,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We got to meet in the end.</b></font>

568
00:42:00,034 --> 00:42:00,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

569
00:42:02,064 --> 00:42:03,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Anyway,</b></font>

570
00:42:03,614 --> 00:42:08,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>what was it that you wanted to tell me the other day, Iketani-san?</b></font>

571
00:42:08,014 --> 00:42:08,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Huh?</b></font>

572
00:42:08,784 --> 00:42:10,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's...</b></font>

573
00:42:10,234 --> 00:42:11,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>well...</b></font>

574
00:42:11,814 --> 00:42:13,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Crap.</b></font>

575
00:42:13,344 --> 00:42:17,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've totally lost my momentum because of how pathetic this situation is.</b></font>

576
00:42:21,704 --> 00:42:23,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>O-oh yeah,</b></font>

577
00:42:23,624 --> 00:42:26,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>you said you had something to say too, Mako-chan.</b></font>

578
00:42:26,554 --> 00:42:27,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What was it about?</b></font>

579
00:42:36,314 --> 00:42:37,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So,</b></font>

580
00:42:37,774 --> 00:42:39,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know it's rather sudden...</b></font>

581
00:42:42,974 --> 00:42:45,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but I'm moving to Tokyo.</b></font>

582
00:42:45,094 --> 00:42:46,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Huh?</b></font>

583
00:42:46,294 --> 00:42:47,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Tokyo?</b></font>

584
00:42:59,834 --> 00:43:05,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There was a promotion where a certain publishing company would sponsor an amateur to drive in races for a year...</b></font>

585
00:43:05,324 --> 00:43:10,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and that person's experiences would be published in a magazine.</b></font>

586
00:43:10,164 --> 00:43:11,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay.</b></font>

587
00:43:11,644 --> 00:43:14,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I applied for the heck of it,</b></font>

588
00:43:15,174 --> 00:43:17,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and for whatever reason...</b></font>

589
00:43:17,544 --> 00:43:19,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You got accepted?</b></font>

590
00:43:21,374 --> 00:43:22,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's amazing!</b></font>

591
00:43:22,634 --> 00:43:24,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're going to be a racer!</b></font>

592
00:43:24,834 --> 00:43:30,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Although it's just a race series sponsored by car makers with only minimal modifications allowed to vehicles...</b></font>

593
00:43:30,584 --> 00:43:32,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's still amazing!</b></font>

594
00:43:32,094 --> 00:43:33,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah,</b></font>

595
00:43:33,154 --> 00:43:37,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I hear that a huge sum of money is needed for someone to race for a full year.</b></font>

596
00:43:38,054 --> 00:43:40,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I couldn't possibly pay for it myself.</b></font>

597
00:43:40,464 --> 00:43:41,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm sure.</b></font>

598
00:43:42,544 --> 00:43:45,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I really wasn't sure,</b></font>

599
00:43:45,024 --> 00:43:47,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but I don't think a chance like this will come my way ever again.</b></font>

600
00:43:51,034 --> 00:43:54,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I just had to talk to you about this, Iketani-san.</b></font>

601
00:43:55,584 --> 00:43:58,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I think it's all thanks to you...</b></font>

602
00:43:58,884 --> 00:44:01,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>that I've been able to keep driving this long, Iketani-san.</b></font>

603
00:44:01,214 --> 00:44:04,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>W-what are you talking about, Mako-chan?</b></font>

604
00:44:04,114 --> 00:44:05,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's not true at all.</b></font>

605
00:44:05,594 --> 00:44:08,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, I don't think I would've had this opportunity</b></font>

606
00:44:09,514 --> 00:44:13,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>if I hadn't met you, Iketani-san.</b></font>

607
00:44:13,974 --> 00:44:16,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh man...</b></font>

608
00:44:18,734 --> 00:44:20,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Either way, I'm glad to hear that.</b></font>

609
00:44:20,934 --> 00:44:22,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Congratulations, Mako-chan.</b></font>

610
00:44:26,124 --> 00:44:30,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't believe that someone I know is going to become a racer!</b></font>

611
00:44:30,474 --> 00:44:34,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll brag about you to all my friends when you become famous!</b></font>

612
00:44:34,954 --> 00:44:37,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When you do, please give me your first autograph.</b></font>

613
00:44:37,164 --> 00:44:40,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh no, what are you talking about?</b></font>

614
00:44:40,504 --> 00:44:42,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, I'm serious.</b></font>

615
00:44:42,054 --> 00:44:43,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm impressed.</b></font>

616
00:44:43,094 --> 00:44:44,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're great, Mako-chan!</b></font>

617
00:44:48,204 --> 00:44:50,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>She's actually happy about it.</b></font>

618
00:44:50,664 --> 00:44:52,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well yeah,</b></font>

619
00:44:52,654 --> 00:44:54,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>why wouldn't she be.</b></font>

620
00:44:54,884 --> 00:44:58,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, I've been doing all the talking,</b></font>

621
00:44:58,414 --> 00:45:00,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but I want to hear what you have to say too, Iketani-san.</b></font>

622
00:45:00,394 --> 00:45:02,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>W-well,</b></font>

623
00:45:02,104 --> 00:45:03,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>what I had to say was...</b></font>

624
00:45:04,764 --> 00:45:06,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This isn't good.</b></font>

625
00:45:06,364 --> 00:45:09,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Compared to what you just told me, it's nothing at all.</b></font>

626
00:45:09,404 --> 00:45:12,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's not true, please tell me!</b></font>

627
00:45:12,284 --> 00:45:15,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, it really was nothing.</b></font>

628
00:45:15,854 --> 00:45:19,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>See, I wanted to properly apologize for what happened last year.</b></font>

629
00:45:19,744 --> 00:45:22,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And it looks like I have your understanding already.</b></font>

630
00:45:22,984 --> 00:45:24,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So it's all right.</b></font>

631
00:45:26,064 --> 00:45:27,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is that so?</b></font>

632
00:45:27,544 --> 00:45:28,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

633
00:45:41,514 --> 00:45:45,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I actually want to tell her, "Don't go."</b></font>

634
00:45:45,044 --> 00:45:45,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But...</b></font>

635
00:45:46,944 --> 00:45:49,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But... I can't do it.</b></font>

636
00:45:52,344 --> 00:45:53,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Iketani-san...</b></font>

637
00:45:54,554 --> 00:45:56,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Mako-chan...</b></font>

638
00:45:56,484 --> 00:46:02,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, I need to call a tow truck to fix up my car and drive it home.</b></font>

639
00:46:02,384 --> 00:46:06,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm sorry, but do you think you can drop me off somewhere near a phone?</b></font>

640
00:46:12,174 --> 00:46:13,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay?</b></font>

641
00:46:33,794 --> 00:46:35,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?!</b></font>

642
00:46:35,114 --> 00:46:39,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So you came back without confessing your feelings?</b></font>

643
00:46:39,154 --> 00:46:40,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I mean,</b></font>

644
00:46:40,834 --> 00:46:43,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>how could I say it under those circumstances?</b></font>

645
00:46:43,084 --> 00:46:47,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You might say that, but your feelings will never reach her if you don't tell her!</b></font>

646
00:46:47,584 --> 00:46:49,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's okay.</b></font>

647
00:46:51,464 --> 00:47:00,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Since Mako-chan's leaving for Tokyo to start racing, confessing my feelings will only trouble her.</b></font>

648
00:47:00,004 --> 00:47:01,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But man...</b></font>

649
00:47:01,344 --> 00:47:04,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It might make me feel good,</b></font>

650
00:47:04,134 --> 00:47:06,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but that's only self-satisfaction.</b></font>

651
00:47:06,564 --> 00:47:10,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This was the right choice when you think about the other person's feelings.</b></font>

652
00:47:16,114 --> 00:47:22,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Telling her, "Give it your best," and cheering her on is the best I can do.</b></font>

653
00:47:23,474 --> 00:47:26,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're too nice...</b></font>

654
00:47:27,664 --> 00:47:28,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Maybe.</b></font>

655
00:47:33,714 --> 00:47:36,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's pretty cold of Iketani.</b></font>

656
00:47:37,694 --> 00:47:41,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I thought he had feelings for you too.</b></font>

657
00:47:41,234 --> 00:47:43,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I really don't get men.</b></font>

658
00:47:43,804 --> 00:47:45,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's okay, Sayuki.</b></font>

659
00:47:45,744 --> 00:47:48,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Now I can move on.</b></font>

660
00:47:48,024 --> 00:47:49,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Really?</b></font>

661
00:47:49,914 --> 00:47:52,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>To be honest, I was worried.</b></font>

662
00:47:52,664 --> 00:47:55,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Life in Tokyo seems tough.</b></font>

663
00:47:55,594 --> 00:48:01,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wasn't confident that a wimp like me could become a racer.</b></font>

664
00:48:01,844 --> 00:48:03,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was hesitant until the last minute,</b></font>

665
00:48:03,974 --> 00:48:09,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so much so that I could've been swayed had someone told me not to go.</b></font>

666
00:48:11,874 --> 00:48:14,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But now I'm embarrassed that I even thought that.</b></font>

667
00:48:14,614 --> 00:48:19,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm sure Iketani-san was cold to me because he saw through all that.</b></font>

668
00:48:21,724 --> 00:48:24,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He gave me a push on the back saying,</b></font>

669
00:48:24,984 --> 00:48:27,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>"Go give it a try with confidence,"</b></font>

670
00:48:27,754 --> 00:48:29,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so that I won't leave any unnecessary regrets over here.</b></font>

671
00:48:30,584 --> 00:48:32,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's what I'd like to think.</b></font>

672
00:48:35,194 --> 00:48:36,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That might be true.</b></font>

673
00:48:36,874 --> 00:48:38,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He does have an admirable side to him like that.</b></font>

674
00:48:38,984 --> 00:48:42,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I get a feeling that's true.</b></font>

675
00:48:46,504 --> 00:48:47,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Iketani,</b></font>

676
00:48:47,794 --> 00:48:49,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>do you really...</b></font>

677
00:48:49,794 --> 00:48:52,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>have no regrets?</b></font>

678
00:48:53,704 --> 00:48:55,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Nope.</b></font>

679
00:48:55,034 --> 00:48:56,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's tough,</b></font>

680
00:48:56,394 --> 00:48:57,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but I have no regrets.</b></font>

681
00:48:58,444 --> 00:49:01,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is how it was supposed to be.</b></font>

682
00:49:10,634 --> 00:49:11,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Mako...</b></font>

683
00:49:19,524 --> 00:49:21,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Good luck!</b></font>

684
00:49:21,614 --> 00:49:24,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I certify your talents.</b></font>

685
00:49:24,904 --> 00:49:25,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah,</b></font>

686
00:49:25,974 --> 00:49:27,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll go as far as I can.</b></font>

687
00:49:28,584 --> 00:49:30,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I won't hesitate anymore.</b></font>

688
00:49:31,404 --> 00:49:34,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So this is the end for Impact Blue.</b></font>

689
00:49:34,634 --> 00:49:36,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's a little sad.</b></font>

690
00:49:53,854 --> 00:49:56,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I need to practice more.</b></font>

691
00:49:56,214 --> 00:50:00,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I blew my tire at a time like that because my skills are still lacking.</b></font>

692
00:50:02,904 --> 00:50:05,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Will you go practice with me, Kenji?</b></font>

693
00:50:05,874 --> 00:50:06,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

694
00:50:26,424 --> 00:50:28,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi told me this before,</b></font>

695
00:50:28,434 --> 00:50:32,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but I guess I push it too far when I get pumped up.</b></font>

696
00:50:34,354 --> 00:50:35,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Next up is the S-curve.</b></font>

697
00:50:35,854 --> 00:50:37,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>All right!</b></font>

698
00:50:45,114 --> 00:50:47,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is the last run for Impact Blue.</b></font>

699
00:50:48,374 --> 00:50:50,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Please take a good look, Sayuki.</b></font>

700
00:50:50,494 --> 00:50:51,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah,</b></font>

701
00:50:51,424 --> 00:50:53,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>give me a refreshing run,</b></font>

702
00:50:53,124 --> 00:50:55,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Impact Blue's shooting star.</b></font>

703
00:51:09,724 --> 00:51:13,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You still have some work to do. You're ballooning out too far to the outside.</b></font>

704
00:51:13,004 --> 00:51:13,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay.</b></font>

705
00:51:14,724 --> 00:51:17,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But this is great.</b></font>

706
00:51:17,844 --> 00:51:20,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When I'm driving like this, I can forget everything.</b></font>

707
00:51:21,374 --> 00:51:23,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I might not be as fast as Takumi,</b></font>

708
00:51:23,524 --> 00:51:25,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but I must be a racer at heart too.</b></font>

709
00:54:29,894 --> 00:54:32,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Street racers...</b></font>

710
00:54:32,774 --> 00:54:36,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>don't need girlfriends!</b></font>

